<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Day 7: Your Weekly Success Report</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .stat-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üèÜ Your First Week - Success Report!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hey <%= name %>,</h2>

            <p>Congratulations! You've completed your first week with LinkedInPulse. Here's what you've accomplished:
            </p>

            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-number">7</div>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">Days of LinkedIn Mastery</p>
            </div>

            <p><strong>üéØ What's Working:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>You've unlocked the power of AI-driven content</li>
                <li>You understand the content strategy fundamentals</li>
                <li>You have access to advanced features</li>
                <li>You're ready to build your personal brand</li>
            </ul>

            <p><strong>üìà Your Next Steps to LinkedIn Success:</strong></p>
            <ol style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li><strong>Consistency is Key:</strong> Post 3x per week minimum</li>
                <li><strong>Engage Authentically:</strong> Comment on others' posts daily</li>
                <li><strong>Track Your Growth:</strong> Monitor engagement in your analytics</li>
                <li><strong>Optimize & Iterate:</strong> Use what works, improve what doesn't</li>
            </ol>

            <div
                style="background-color: #fff3e0; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <strong style="color: #e65100;">üî• Special Insight:</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #e65100;">Users who post consistently in their first month see 5x
                    more profile views and 3x more connection requests. Your momentum starts now!</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:3000' %>/dashboard/analytics"
                    class="cta-button">
                    View My Analytics ‚Üí
                </a>
            </div>

            <p>We're here if you need anything. Reply to this email with questions!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Here's to your LinkedIn success!<br><strong>The LinkedInPulse Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> LinkedInPulse. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>